title: Week 14 recap
itunes:title: Week 14 recap
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler, and Dan Hanzus – break down all the Week 14 action including the Patriots climbing to the top of the AFC with a win over the Texans, and the Panthers clinching a first-round bye after shutting out the Falcons. Plus, the heroes check in with Around the NFL correspondents Conor Orr and Kevin Patra to get their takes on who wins the NFC East, and the Panthers chances of winning out
